Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哪一个袋子? - 那个LV手提袋呀\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Any idea which one, Miss Suzanne? - The Louis Vuitton duffel, right on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没看到\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I don't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是瞎了吗? 在侧袋里头 快找呀\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Just use your fucking eyes! It's in the side pocket! Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干了什么好事?...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What have you done? What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猪头呀 如果你帮他就脱不了关系\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No, fool! If you help him, you assume responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本来就是我的错 放开我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It is my responsibility. Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Alice? Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干了什么好事?...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What have you done? What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看她\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽车驾驶在行驶中...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The driver of every motor vehicle involved in any manner of accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涉及任何交通事故 应该在十天内...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...originating from the operation of a vehicle shall, within 10 days...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你车上有毛巾吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You got a towel or something in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来帮我找\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Okay. Come help me look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.37,0:09:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在车祸发生十天内...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}... within 10 days of the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽车驾驶在行驶中 涉及任何交通事故...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...if you are operating a vehicle and it should, at any time, involve...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 待在这儿 别让她淋湿了 - 不会有事 老婆\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Stay here. Keep her dry. - It's okay. It's okay, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 快开门 我要用手机 - 不要\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Open the door! We need the phone. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆 没事了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Sweetheart, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆 没事了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Honey, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 把你的手机给我 - 收不到讯号\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Give me the goddamn phone! - The phone is dead, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生会把你治好 你不会有事\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You're gonna be fine. You're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她一直流血不止 - 天啊怎么回事?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- She won't stop bleeding. - Jesus. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了车祸 我能借用电话吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}There was an accident. May I please use your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我能借用电话吗? - 当然了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Please use your phone? - Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 一下大雨电话就不通\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Shit. I'm not getting a line. It happens in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话打不出去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The phone doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往东走三十里是圣朱德医院\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}St. Jude's has 24-hour emergency, 30 miles east.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖坐下来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You sit here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续压着伤口 我去找救护车\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Keep pressure on the wound. I'll be back with an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里比连锁旅馆更糟 不过你得凑和凑和\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Sorry. It's a step down from the Ramada, but it'll have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不住在这儿 你疯啦?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I am not staying here. Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的车 你是我的司机 快把袋子放回去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}This is my car. You work for me. Get those bags back in this car now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她被车撞到一直流血 但我也是病人耶\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I understand the bleeding person has a medical condition, but so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有支气管扩张症 我待在这儿会窒息而死\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}My lung walls have depleted cilia. If I stay here, I could asphyxiate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要熄火 拜托拜托...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No, please, please, please, please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停车 求求你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Stop. Please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的车泡水了 能搭便车吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Hi. I'm sorry, my car is stuck. Can I get a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,""存在与虚无"沙特着"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你往东开去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You know you're going east.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去医院\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Hospital's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那儿淹大水 死路一条\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's flooded. I mean, it's a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 我得试一试\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Yeah, well, if you don't mind, I gotta try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十元付现\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Okay, that will be $30 cash, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前不是那个大明星吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Didn't you use to be that actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间好不好?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Wow. - Now, is that a nice room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很快就走 不过我还是要好房间\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Because though I am leaving soon, I still would prefer a nice room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最舒服的房间\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Your nicest...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你帮帮忙\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...if that is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八号房很舒服\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Eight's very cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就跟你说了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I tried to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停车 你过不去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Hey! Hey, stop! There's no way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停车 你过不去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}There's no way through! No way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 小路 醒醒 - 什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Lou, wake up. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么? - 你有手机吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- What? - Do you have a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁呀?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Who wants to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有位女士出车祸受重伤\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}There's been an accident, a bad one. A lady's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我需要一支手机 - 朋友 放轻松\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- We need a cell phone right now. - Dude, slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄 我们又不认识你 也没看到有车祸\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}First, we don't know who you are. Second, we don't see an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我听好 老兄 我今天衰毙了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Listen to me, dude, I'm having a really fucked-up, wet, bad fucking day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有手机就马上给我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}So if you have a cell phone, give it to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没手机啦 快放开我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Dude, we don't have a cell phone, so could you just let go of me now? !
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就载我们到另一边\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I need you to give me a lift in the other direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一边淹水的情况更严重\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's flooded that way too. It's worse than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉妮 打开后车厢 让他们上车\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Ginny, pop the trunk. Let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们上车\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Hey. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 电话还是不通吗? - 对 你的林肯房车呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Phone still dead? - Yeah. Where's your Lincoln?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在两里路外泡水 另一边也淹大水\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Stuck in a run-off two miles down the road. The other way's fucked too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们载我跟那位小姐一程\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The kids gave us a lift. The girl was stranded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 有别的捷径吗? - 她是妓女吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Is there another way out? - Is she a hooker?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有没有捷径?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Hey! Is there a back road?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨这么大 你走不了五百尺\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Where do you think the water's going? You wouldn't get 500 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 那位女士情况怎样? - 我不晓得 他们在四号房\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- How's the woman? - I don't know. They're in number 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"乱葬冢"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这儿不是给人休息的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm sorry. We don't rent rooms by the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好笑 这儿还有吃的吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Funny. You still serving food?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转角有一台自动贩卖机 请自便\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Vending machines are around the corner. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十元付现 出示身份证\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Rooms are 30 bucks in advance with picture ID. You need one room or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要一间或两间? 我在跟你讲话 请你看着我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Excuse me. I was talking to you. I'd appreciate it if you looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢看到贱货\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Well, I don't like looking at trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被困在这儿 今晚走不了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We're a little stuck here, George. I don't think we can get out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她一直发抖 - 她休克了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- She just keeps shaking. - She's in shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 让我看看 - 什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Let me take a look. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太太有带针线盒吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Did your wife pack a sewing kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有 No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉妮 等一下\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Ginny, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六号房\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少这是幸运号码\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}At least we got a good number.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你有感觉到吗? - 感觉到什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Did you feel that? - Feel what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一股寒意\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是老板吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Are you the manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是看守所的罗德警官 我在押解一名人犯\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm Officer Rhodes, Corrections. I'm transporting a prisoner here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以拒绝为我们服务\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The law gives you the right to refuse us service...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是淹大水 我想要一间房间\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...but the roads are flooded. I could use a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是紧急状况 - 你车上有无线电吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- It's an emergency. - You got a radio in that car?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他是谁? - 他是司机 出了车祸\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Who's this? - Limo driver, had an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人受重伤 要叫救护车\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I got a lady pretty banged up. I could use an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,442号警车请求医疗协助\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Four-four-two requesting medical.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,442号警车请求医疗协助\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Four-four-two requesting medical.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有讯号 一直都是这样\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Nothing. It's been like this for the past hour.
