Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.67,0:47:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他让一个杀人犯脱逃\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}The one who's managed to lose a convicted killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.04,0:48:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人很龟毛耶\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You're a complicated cat, Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.94,0:48:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No. Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.75,0:48:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得有\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.25,0:48:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你几月出生?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What month were you born?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.22,0:48:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 五月 - 金牛座\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- May. - Taurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.19,0:48:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一样\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.30,0:48:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在哪儿当过差? - 洛杉矶\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Where were you a cop? - Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.50,0:48:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被炒鱿鱼还是辞职不干?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Were you fired or did you quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.07,0:48:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请长期病假\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I took medical leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.87,0:48:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当警察让我生病\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It was making me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.84,0:48:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜我是受不了那种压力\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I burned out, I guess. Wasn't up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.22,0:48:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天我接到报案...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}One day I got a call...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.79,0:48:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想跳楼自杀\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...for a jumper.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.29,0:48:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个墨西哥裔女生\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}A young Mexican girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.80,0:49:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她得了爱滋病还怀了身孕\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Pregnant, infected with AIDS, totally strung-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.87,0:49:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的是走投无路\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}She was truly one of the doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.47,0:49:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请她让我把她抱下来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I asked her to come in off the ledge and into my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.94,0:49:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她问我她有什么好活的? 活着有什么意义?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}She asked me why she should bother living.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.39,0:49:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么说?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.79,0:49:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们受过训练要说一些话\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I was trained to tell her lots of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.73,0:49:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是你要为亲人着想之类的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Her dreams, all the people who'd miss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.90,0:49:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却犹豫了一秒\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But for a second, I hesitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.94,0:49:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看出来了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And she saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.21,0:49:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那短短的一秒 我想不出活着有什么意义\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Within that second, I couldn't think of one optimistic thing to say to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.48,0:49:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是她展开双臂 奋力一跳\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}So she spread her arms and jumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.89,0:50:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始会头痛...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I started getting headaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.50,0:50:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来经常失去意识\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...and eventually started blacking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.90,0:50:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就请病假\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}So I filed for medical.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.12,0:50:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.56,0:50:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.66,0:50:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗德!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Rhodes!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.63,0:50:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 更糟 只有杂讯 - 女明星的房间钥匙呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- It's worse. Nothing but static! - Where's that key from the actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.21,0:50:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这在那小子身上找到\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}This was on the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.18,0:50:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 这算是倒数吗? - 赖瑞\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- What is it, some kind of countdown? - Larry!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.48,0:51:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在干什么? 赖瑞 过来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What the fuck is he doing? Larry, come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.72,0:51:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快过来 你在干嘛?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Come over here, man. What are you doing? Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.93,0:51:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在干什么? - 我只是去拿东西\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- What are you doing? - I just went to get something.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.96,0:51:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们叫你看守人犯 你到办公室干嘛?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We told you to watch the guy. What are you doing in your office?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.47,0:51:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是去拿东西\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I just went to get something.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.10,0:51:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家旅馆有几副钥匙? 看着我 有几副?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}How many sets of keys are there to this place? Look at me. How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.01,0:51:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 两副 一支万能钥匙 - 我的老天\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Two and a master set. - Oh, my fucking God!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.28,0:51:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赖瑞 你这大混蛋 混帐东西 给我进来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Larry, you mother... ! You son of a... ! Get the fuck in here! Get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.72,0:51:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么杀死我的人犯?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Why did you kill him? Why did you kill my con?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.49,0:51:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇靠这是谁干的? 人不是我杀的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Holy shit! Who did that? Jesus Christ, I didn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.56,0:51:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放屁 你在撒谎\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Bullshit! You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.33,0:51:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是你的球棒 - 对 但不是我干的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- It's your bat sticking out of his throat! - I know, but I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.40,0:51:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查每一道门\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Check the doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.30,0:51:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不是我干的 - 看看他\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- I didn't do it! - Look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.10,0:51:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你干嘛杀他? - 你跑出去干嘛?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Why'd you kill him? - Why were you outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.51,0:51:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你为什么出去? - 我很害怕\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Why'd you leave him? - I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.71,0:51:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 怕什么? - 你们不会明白\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- What were you scared of? - You wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.11,0:51:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来听听\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Try me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.74,0:52:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你为什么杀死他? - 我没有\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Why'd you kill my con? - I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.68,0:52:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道这是... 我只是回办公室而已\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I don't know how... I went to my office, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.75,0:52:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你干嘛离开? - 这是你的钥匙吗? 八号房?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Why'd you leave him? - This your key? Number 8?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.59,0:52:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十九八? 这是你的钥匙\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Ten, nine, eight, huh? This is your key!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.39,0:52:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能这么说 这不是我的钥匙\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You can't say that! Those aren't my keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.53,0:52:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是栽贼耶 你看看\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}That's like leading the witness or something. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.66,0:52:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些才是我的钥匙 你瞧\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}These are my keys, okay? These are my keys. You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.90,0:52:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是女明星的古驰钱包\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You got a Gucci wallet? It's the actress's.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.44,0:52:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是拿了她的钱包 不过是在她死后\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Yes, I took her wallet. Afterwards. After she died!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.01,0:52:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她死了以后 我没杀她 我也没杀他\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Afterwards, all right? I didn't kill her. And I didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.58,0:52:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 放开她 - 退后 你们别想嫁祸给我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Let her go, Larry. - Get back! You won't pin this on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.52,0:52:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 提姆西? - 快把他带走\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Timothy? - Get him out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.72,0:52:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 把刀子放下 - 人不是我杀的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Put it down. - I didn't hurt anybody. No one!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.26,0:52:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我讨厌这婊子 你们敢过来...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}But I don't like cheap fucking whores! If you take one more step...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.79,0:52:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.30,0:53:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把他弄走\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Get it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.11,0:53:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.22,0:53:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭卡车 快发动呀\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Come on, you little bitch. Please fucking start.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.56,0:53:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 可恶 - 喂!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Goddamn it! - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.23,0:53:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赖瑞 停车\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Larry, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.73,0:53:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.67,0:53:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 赖瑞! - 给我让开 我什么都没做\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Larry! - Get out of my way, I didn't do shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.34,0:53:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提姆西! 提姆西!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Timothy! Timothy!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.50,0:54:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被告是四级解离性身分病患...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}An insanity plea was refused by the court...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.03,0:54:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法庭却拒绝承认他的精神错乱\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...despite the fact that my client is a certifiable Axis IV dissociative.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.71,0:54:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到现在对他所犯的罪 都毫不知情\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}To this day, he remains unaware of the crimes for which he was convicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.54,0:54:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1986年最高法院判决...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}In 1986, the Supreme Court ruled decisively that states cannot execute...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.48,0:54:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,州政府不能处决精神错乱人犯\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...a person who does not understand why he's being put to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.92,0:54:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他签下自白书\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He signed a confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.39,0:54:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是他亲口对我说的供词 - 还有...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- He didn't just sign it, he dictated it. - Thirdly...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.09,0:54:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是麦肯的日记 被藏在物证室\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...Malcolm's diaries found misfiled in state evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.76,0:54:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这上面有他在命案前的记录\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}this notebook contains entries made just before the murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.90,0:54:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重点是他的笔迹有很大的改变\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Important to note are the spectacular changes in handwriting style...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.41,0:54:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有语调和观点\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...tone, point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.34,0:54:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是多重人格的内心世界\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What you are looking at are the private thoughts of several different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.35,0:54:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让马医师进一步说明\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}With permission, Dr. Mallick will elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.28,0:54:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.05,0:54:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人 解离性身分 也就是多重人格...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Your Honor, there is no universally efficacious treatment...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.96,0:55:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有有效的治疗方法\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...for Dissociative Identity Disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.96,0:55:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能试着整合这些多重人格\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}In theory, one attempts to move the patient towards integration.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.40,0:55:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 让病患破碎的心灵愈合 - 法官大人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- A folding of their fractured psyche. - Your Honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.44,0:55:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.26,0:55:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是场意外\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No! What you saw was an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.12,0:55:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他突然冲出来 我没有杀人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He ran out in front of me! I'm not a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.46,0:55:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷冻库有一具尸体\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}There's a dead body in your freezer, Larry.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.70,0:55:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我发现他死了 我没杀他 - 少来了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- I didn't kill him. I found him like that. - Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.40,0:55:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们听我说 上个月我在赌城输个精光\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Listen! Listen! I was in Vegas last month and I lost everything, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.07,0:55:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输个精光\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.47,0:55:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走投无路只好往西走\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I drove west. I didn't know where to go, but I was running on empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.27,0:55:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的车没油了只好来这儿\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...so I pulled in here at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.88,0:55:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油站没人 所以我就直接...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And there was no one at the station, so I came over to the office...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.38,0:55:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走进办公室\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...and I walked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.35,0:56:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板就坐在办公桌\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And there, sitting at that desk right there, was the manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.39,0:56:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一头栽进冷冻披萨暴毙\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...facedown in a Banquet Potpie. Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.22,0:56:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他一定是心脏病发作 - 这未免太扯了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Heart attack or something. - Banquet Potpie!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.69,0:56:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晓得他死了有多久\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He'd been sitting there for God knows how long.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.43,0:56:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候突然有一个人来住房\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}All of a sudden, this auto-parts salesman pulls up, looking for a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.63,0:56:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我身无分文...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I didn't have a fucking dime...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.07,0:56:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就收了三十元给他房间\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...so I took his 30 and gave him one.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.84,0:56:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿了钥匙给他一间房间\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I just took the key from the wall and gave him a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.31,0:56:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我那么做不对 但是我没钱 只好那么做\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Maybe that was wrong, but I was broke, and that's what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.65,0:56:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就回办公室\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Then I came back in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.25,0:56:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬走赖瑞的尸体 他也叫赖瑞\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...and I moved Larry's body... His name was Larry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.02,0:56:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把他放进冷冻库\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I put him in the freezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.26,0:56:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气很热 我不想让他发臭\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I wasn't trying to hide him. It was hot out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.16,0:56:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想等他的家人来找他\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I thought it was the best place for him till his family or someone came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.93,0:56:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的家人没找上门...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Only no one did...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.94,0:56:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人却络绎不绝\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...except more guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.87,0:56:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只好让他们住进来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}So I checked them in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.64,0:57:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都很满意\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And they all seemed happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.31,0:57:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就待了下来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...so I just stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.02,0:57:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省省吧 这全是胡扯淡\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Cry me a river. This is a total crock of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.35,0:57:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 才不是 - 承认吧 你杀死他\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- No, it's not! - Admit it, you killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.96,0:57:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也杀死人犯她老公...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Just like you killed my con. Just like you killed her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.89,0:57:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他的女明星 承认吧\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Just like you killed his actress. Just admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.70,0:57:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 说"人是我杀的" - 别说了 他受不了了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Say it, "I killed them." - Stop it! He can't take any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.57,0:57:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了 我们抓到凶手了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Everything is okay now. Everything is fine. We got the guy. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.30,0:57:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不能确定 - 什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- I don't know what we got. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.21,0:57:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两小时前也以为抓到凶手...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We thought we got the guy two hours ago, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.84,0:57:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 凶手就是这家伙\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You believe this shit? It's him! It's this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.38,0:57:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拿刀威胁你 记得吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He had a knife to your neck, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.68,0:57:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这故事太夸张 搞不好是真的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}His story's so unbelievable, I think it just might be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.65,0:57:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说的有道理\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}She's got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.09,0:57:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都疯了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You guys are crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.46,0:57:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为这儿是乱葬塚\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Maybe it's the burial ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.56,0:57:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.43,0:57:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地方全都是墓地\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Read the brochure in there. It's all around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.77,0:58:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百年前印第安人被迫迁移\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}A hundred years ago, the government moved these Indians here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.04,0:58:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿缺水他们全都渴死\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}They all died because there was no water.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.34,0:58:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他们就回来报仇吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Now they're coming back to life like sea monkeys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.91,0:58:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太扯了 小姑娘\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Come on. Give me a break, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.05,0:58:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 别这样 罗德 - 你才别这样\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Just take it easy, Rhodes. - You know, you take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.55,0:58:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从一开始就在发号施令\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You've tried to run this show all night. Giving orders, pointing fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.42,0:58:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还把错归在我的人犯头上 结果他也挂了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You blamed my con for everything, and he ends up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.59,0:58:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你 凶手就是他 大家都看到他撞死乔治\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm telling you, it's him! We all saw him run down George.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.80,0:58:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他偷走的钱包在那儿\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Your actress's wallet is right there. She's dead, there's the wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.43,0:58:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 这还不够吗? - 住嘴 别说了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- What more do you want? - Stop it! Please shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.37,0:58:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你们该怎么做\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}All right. You want a plan? Here's the plan, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.67,0:58:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也别乱跑 我们都待在这儿等天亮\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No one's gonna move. We'll stay here, like this, in this room until dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.08,0:58:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人可以离开\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No one leaves, no one moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.41,0:58:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他敢乱来我就毙了他\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And if he tries anything, I'm gonna shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.55,0:58:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想闯进来我也毙了它\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And if something out there comes in here, I'll shoot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.92,0:58:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想造反我也毙了你们\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And if anyone of us tries anything, I'll shoot them!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.99,0:58:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们懂了 - 很好\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- We get it. - Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.29,0:59:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提姆西? 提姆西?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Timmy? Timmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.93,0:59:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要留在这儿 - 没关系\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- You need to stay in here with us. - It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.84,0:59:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一部电影拍十个人流落荒岛...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Remember that movie where the 10 strangers went to an island...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.31,0:59:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一个接一个死去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...and then they all died one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.88,0:59:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他们都有一个共通点\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...and then it turned out they weren't strangers, they all had a connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.41,0:59:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他们害的人回来找他们算帐\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}They all messed with the wrong guy, and he was getting revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.82,0:59:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.95,0:59:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们也有共通点\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I'm just saying maybe there's a connection between all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.46,0:59:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.36,1:00:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们都在内华达州 - 闭嘴\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- We're all in Nevada. - Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.06,1:00:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算把人犯押解到哪儿?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Where were you going with your con when you pulled in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.04,1:00:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡森市\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Carson City. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.97,1:00:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回佛州老家 你呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I was going home to Florida. Where were you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.21,1:00:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要载女明星到洛杉矶\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I was taking the actress to L.A.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.45,1:00:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在佛州出生\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I was born in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.08,1:00:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是凶手 给我乖乖闭嘴\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Since you been in that chair, no one's died, so shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.99,1:00:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都可能是凶手\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No one's died since we've all been here!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.59,1:00:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 小乖乖 坐下来 - 佛州的哪儿?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Hey, sweetie, sit down. - Where in Florida, Larry?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.76,1:00:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在哪儿出生? - 你们突然变成好友了吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Where in Florida? - Friends now, huh? Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.43,1:00:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 波克郡 - 我也是\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Polk County. - That's where I was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.93,1:00:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哪一个城镇? - 桑树镇\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Which town? - Mulberry.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.44,1:00:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我是防霜镇 - 怪不得你会离开\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Frostproof. - No wonder you left.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.04,1:00:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个小镇叫防霜?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}There's a town called Frostproof?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.51,1:00:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那儿种柳橙 防霜也是小镇的宣传口号\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}They grow oranges. The name doubles as a slogan.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.61,1:00:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我巴不得离开 你干嘛回去?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I danced hallelujah the day I left Polk. Why would you wanna go back?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.55,1:01:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到一片果园要出售\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I found a grove for sale on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.69,1:01:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一千两百棵莱姆和柳橙树\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Nine acres, 1200 trees. Limes and oranges.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.79,1:01:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲介跟我说土壤需要磷...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}According to the realtor, the soil needs a few tills, phosphorous...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.53,1:01:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要除除草 不过那块地很不错\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...lanes need reading, but it's real good land.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.97,1:01:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.44,1:01:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来很好\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.06,1:01:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Ed?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.77,1:01:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她死了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.56,1:02:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他带出去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.86,1:02:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 小乖乖\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Come on. Come on, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.60,1:02:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.44,1:02:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 在哪儿找到的? - 就在地上\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Where'd you get that? - Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.12,1:02:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没道理 她死于意外\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}This doesn't make any sense. She died from an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.56,1:02:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔治也是死于意外 如果你相信赖瑞的话\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}George was an accident, if you believe Larry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.00,1:02:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七号钥匙呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Where is seven?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.10,1:03:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒车\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Back it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.31,1:03:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我就说凶手不是我 - 不可能\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- See, I told you it wasn't me! - That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.18,1:03:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就站在那儿 我们都亲眼看到发生什么事\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I was standing right there. I saw what happened. We all saw what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.45,1:03:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他突然冲出来 没有人料得到\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He ran out. Nobody could have known he was gonna do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.15,1:03:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手不是人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No one human.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.62,1:03:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 凶手是恶灵\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We're back to that again? It's the spirits, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.26,1:03:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是冷冻库那家伙的冤魂\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Maybe it's the ghost of the guy that Larry put in the freezer.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.26,1:04:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把我解开\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Somebody untie me. Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.37,1:04:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手不是我\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You know it wasn't me. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.37,1:04:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 听好 - 我们得离开... - 听好 - 我们得离开... - Listen.\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- We gotta get out... - Listen. - We gotta get out...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.34,1:04:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她带着孩子快走\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Take her car and get out. You, her and the kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.74,1:04:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无处可去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}There's nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.14,1:04:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的车剩多少油? - 半缸油\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- How much gas do you have? - Half a tank.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.34,1:04:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就够开到天亮\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You can drive till dawn on that. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.61,1:04:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到淹水就往另一头开\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}When you get to where it's flooded, go the other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.45,1:04:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我办不到\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I don't know if I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.98,1:04:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着孩子快走吧\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Get the kid and go. Right now. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.29,1:04:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提姆\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Timmy.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.45,1:04:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提姆 我们走\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Timmy, come on. Let's go. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.26,1:04:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.59,1:04:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们不能走 - 这边走\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- They can't leave! - This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.49,1:04:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大雨过后再见\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We'll see you when the storm breaks.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.63,1:04:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不能走 给我回来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Hey! Hey! They can't leave! Where are they going? Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.13,1:04:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们非走不可 快走吧\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Go, go, go! They're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.90,1:04:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们不能离开 - 走吧!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- They're not leaving. - Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.44,1:04:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在四个人死了之后 你不能让嫌犯脱逃\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You can't let suspects leave after four people have been killed!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.34,1:04:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你真的认为他们是嫌犯吗? - 他们不能走\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- You really think they're suspects? - They're not leaving!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.01,1:04:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.05,1:04:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉妮!\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Ginny!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.89,1:04:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭火器 这儿有灭火器吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Extinguishers. Larry, you got a fire extinguisher?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.12,1:05:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 灭火器在哪儿? - 后面\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Fire extinguisher! Where? - Back there!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.65,1:05:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车上没有人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Nobody in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.92,1:05:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们都被火化了\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Maybe it got so hot, they got cremated.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.09,1:05:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也会留下骨灰\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}There'd be something left.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.43,1:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的错\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You did this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.43,1:05:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫他们上车\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You did this! You told them to get into the car!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.77,1:05:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴了吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.36,1:06:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的尸体呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.96,1:07:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.30,1:07:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我投降\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I give up!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.70,1:07:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我投降 你到底想要什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I give up! What the hell do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.51,1:07:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这大变态 你要我们怎样?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What do you want, you sick bastard? What the fuck do you want from us?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.45,1:07:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下礼拜就满三十岁 我只想回老家...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I am turning 30 next week and I just want to go home...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.38,1:07:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种柳丁\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...and grow oranges!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.99,1:07:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你下礼拜生日?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's my birthday next week. The 10th.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.89,1:07:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样 五月十日\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}It's my birthday next week. The 10th.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.37,1:07:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.84,1:08:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.07,1:08:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.15,1:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔治约克 五月十日\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}George York, May 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.85,1:08:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝约克 五月十日\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Alice York, May 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.95,1:08:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萝琳苏珊 五月十日\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Caroline Suzanne, May 10
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.82,1:08:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉妮和路易西安那 五月十日\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Ginny and Lou Isiana, May 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.56,1:08:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赖瑞华盛顿 五月十日\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Me, Larry Washington, May fucking 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.03,1:08:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只有十兆分之一的机率\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What are the odds? Must be 10 trillion-to-one.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.50,1:08:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.98,1:08:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 电箱在哪里? - 旅馆的另一边\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Where's the fuse box, Larry? - Other side of the building.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.72,1:08:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉妮和路易西安那\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Ginny and Lou Isiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.36,1:08:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维吉尼亚和路易西安那\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Virginia and Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.33,1:09:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萝琳...卡罗莱纳\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Caroline, Carolina.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.40,1:09:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴黎内华达\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Paris Nevada
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.57,1:09:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔治约克\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}George York.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.17,1:09:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赖瑞华盛顿\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Larry Washington.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.81,1:09:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗德...罗德岛\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Rhodes, Rhode Island.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.32,1:09:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德达科塔\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Ed Dakota.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.00,1:09:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我走上楼梯 我看到一个不在那儿的人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}When I was going up the stairs I met a man who wasn't there
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.64,1:09:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天他又不在那里\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He wasn't there again today
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.18,1:09:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他会永远消失\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I wish I wish he'd go away
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.81,1:09:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.05,1:09:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在跟谁讲话?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Who am I speaking to right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.75,1:09:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首诗是哪儿学来的?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Where did you learn that poem?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.16,1:10:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在跟谁讲话?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Who am I speaking to? Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.73,1:10:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我 你现在是谁?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Who am I speaking to right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.60,1:10:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Doc?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.04,1:10:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 艾德华? - 发生什么事?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Edward? - What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.64,1:10:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 安静 - 他听得到我们说话?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Please be quiet. - He can hear what we're saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.61,1:10:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然听得到你说话\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Of course I can hear what you're fucking saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.18,1:10:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爽约了 你跑去哪儿?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Edward, you missed your last appointment. Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.42,1:10:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我又失去意识吗? - 仔细想\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Did I black out again? - Try and think back.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.89,1:10:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.53,1:10:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开车送一个女明星...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}All right. I was driving this actress...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.70,1:10:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被困在汽车旅馆 有一场暴风雨\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...and we got stuck at the motel. There was a storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.77,1:10:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被暴风雨困住出不去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}We couldn't get out because of the storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.61,1:10:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那儿发生什么事?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What happened at the motel?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.61,1:10:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一个一个死去\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}People started dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.51,1:10:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这没有道理 他们的尸体...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}And then their bodies... It didn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.72,1:11:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都消失不见\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}They disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.99,1:11:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要给你看一样东西\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Edward, I'd like to show something to you, if I may.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.96,1:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认得这个人吗?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Do you recognize this man?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.30,1:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认得\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.37,1:11:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是麦肯芮佛\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}That man, Edward, is Malcolm Rivers.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.37,1:11:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的一生很坎坷 他四年前...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He's had a very troubled life. He was arrested four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.14,1:11:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残暴地夺走六条人命 所以被捕入狱\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...and convicted of the murder of six people in a violent rampage.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.98,1:11:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是他干的 - 警探 别这样\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- He did this. - Detective, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.38,1:11:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德华 听我说\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Edward, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.42,1:11:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当一个小孩遭受重大打击 他的心灵会严重受创...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}When faced with an intense trauma, a child's mind may fracture...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.49,1:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成人格的分裂\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...creating disassociated identities.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.86,1:11:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是麦肯芮佛的遭遇\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}That's exactly what happened to Malcolm Rivers.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.46,1:11:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有一般人所谓的...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He developed a condition that is commonly known...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.03,1:11:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重人格症\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...as Multiple Personality Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.18,1:12:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么跟我说这些?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.38,1:12:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Because you, Edward...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.81,1:12:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他多重人格中的一个\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...are one of his personalities.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.42,1:12:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.64,1:12:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天 你把我的脸怎么了?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Jesus Christ! What the fuck did you do to my face?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.08,1:12:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 冷静下来 - 我的脸呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Keep calm. - Where is my face?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.94,1:12:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 这就是你的脸 - 我为什么被绑起来?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- That is your face. - Why am I tied up?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.61,1:12:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 冷静点 - 我的脸呢?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Keep calm. - Where is... ?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.38,1:12:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 请冷静 - 天啊\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Please. - Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.08,1:12:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我的脸呢? - 保持冷静\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Where is my face? - Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.42,1:12:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要保持冷静 我为什么被绑起来?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No! I'm not gonna stay calm! Why am I tied up like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.29,1:12:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人是谁? 汽车旅馆发生什么事?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Who are all these people? What happened at the motel?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.93,1:12:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们人呢? - 他们并不存在\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Where is everybody? - They don't exist, Edward.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.13,1:12:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是麦肯小时候分裂的人格\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You were all created by Malcolm as a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.76,1:12:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在骗人 - 想想你知道的\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- You're a liar! - Consider what you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.47,1:12:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 每个人的姓氏都是美国州名 - 不\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- Everyone named after a state. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.00,1:13:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都同一天生日 你也经常失去意识\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Everyone sharing the same birthday. Your blackouts.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.64,1:13:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当过警察\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}No! I was a cop!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.28,1:13:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在洛杉矶当过六年警察\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I was a cop in the Rampart Division of L.A.P.D. for six years.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.18,1:13:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Edward, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.38,1:13:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住在好莱坞的公寓大楼\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I live in Hollywood, in a studio apartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.95,1:13:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不住在那儿 - 我住在那儿\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}- You don't live there. - I do live there!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.59,1:13:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不存在\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}You don't live anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.69,1:13:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很难接受 但是你在镜子中看到的脸\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I know this is difficult to accept, but the face you saw in that mirror...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.93,1:13:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是你巴黎赖瑞...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...is the face I've always seen when I talk to Edward or Paris or Larry...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.40,1:13:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你今晚遇到每一个人的脸\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...or anyone else you've met tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.50,1:13:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦肯正在接受药物治疗\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Malcolm is in the midst of a medical treatment.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.60,1:13:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的多重人格被迫互相面对\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}One which forces all his identities to confront one another for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.34,1:13:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道一定会有暴力行为\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I knew there would be violence...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.05,1:13:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的多重人格也会减少\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...and with it, the number of the identities would be reduced.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.62,1:13:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减少?\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}Reduced?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.69,1:13:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚你见到的人格...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}One of the personalities you've met tonight, Edward...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.66,1:13:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中有一个在四年前杀人\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...committed those murders four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.93,1:14:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟你一样控制麦肯的身体\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}He took control of Malcolm's body, as you have now...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.87,1:14:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后犯下残暴的谋杀案 十九个小时后...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...and released an unspeakable rage. And in 19 hours...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.24,1:14:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦肯将为这些行为被处决\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...Malcolm Rivers will be put to death because of those actions...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.97,1:14:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非我能说服这个人...\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...unless I can convince that man...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.01,1:14:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手已经消失\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}...that the killer is gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.68,1:14:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不行转换人格 艾德华\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I need you to stay with me. Edward?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.29,1:14:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你帮我 我要你帮我完成这件事\N{\3c&H000000&}{\fs13}I need your help. I need your help to finish this.
